N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 19 ยง 812.6 - Review of applications

State Regulations

After receipt of the application the commissioner shall
review the same and shall: (a) Make a
determination as to whether the proposal is practical, logical, reasonable and
satisfactory in scope. (b) Advise
the county of his determination. Notes
